              Annual Report Electronic Submission Instructions


                                Accessibility

     ORI places a wide variety of materials and links on its website to
     provide helpful information on its programs to the public. However,
     the information is subject to verification, updating, and
     correction, and ORI will not be bound by inaccurate or untimely
     statements. Also, individual facts or circumstances may make any
     general statement inapplicable or incorrect. For official statements
     of law and policy, please consult the relevant laws, regulations,
     rulings, or appropriate ORI publications.
     Questions/suggestions about this web page?   Webmaster
